<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ka nunnak le ka dawtnak kha, Nangmah sinah khan kan pek ko, Nangmah
 bia ka ngaih lai, Bawipa, A ka Khamhbawi Jesuh.

[C1]
   Keimah a ka Khamhtu caah Ka nunnak kha ka hman ko lai, Keimah ka
   lung aa lawm ngaingai, A ka Khamhbawi Jesuh.

[V2]
 Nangmah biak awkah ka um cang, Ka nunnak ca nang na thi cang, Tu hnu
 ah kan lawmh chinchin lai, Maw ka Khamhtu Jesuh.

[C2]
   Keimah a ka Khamhtu caah Ka nunnak kha ka hman ko lai, Keimah ka
   lung aa lawm ngaingai, A ka Khamhbawi Jesuh.

[V3]
 Ka thlarau khamh awkah, Bawipa, Kal-va-ry tlang cungah na thi, Ka pum
 dihlak nangmah kan pek, A ka Khamhbawi Jesuh.

[C3]
   Keimah a ka Khamhtu caah Ka nunnak kha ka hman ko lai, Keimah ka
   lung aa lawm ngaingai, A ka Khamhbawi Jesuh.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>NA CA'H KA NUNG LAI CH371</title>
<hymn_number>371</hymn_number>
</song>